  "title": "Kroko‘s Rock Candy",
  "description": "Adds Rock Candy ores in your world",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Kroko's Rock Candy Mod for 1.15.2 - 1.16.2 requires&nbsp;CoalAPI!&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/coalapi\" rel=\"nofollow\">Download it here</a></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This mod adds 10 delicious flavors of Rock Candy<br />You can then condense 9 of the same colored candy into a block to create armor and tools.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Just holding the rock candy tools in your hand or wearing the full armor set gives you buffs!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">5 types of rock candy ore can be found<br />Combine those 5 into 5 additional types of unique rock candy!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">So, grab a pickaxe and start hunting for your brand-new food source in the underground!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This Mod is a Unofficial Port from the <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/dralards-rock-candy-mod\">Dralard's Rock Candy Mod</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Recipes:</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Here is a list of the recipes included with this Mod.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">(Gifs from the <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/dralards-rock-candy-mod\">Original Site</a>)</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://puu.sh/iX2AK/2a84c9cef0.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"352\" height=\"173\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://puu.sh/iTPr8/3a227b2c3f.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"352\" height=\"1820\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Credits for the GIFs goes to Shadow3654.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Mod Showcases:</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">/</p>\n<div id=\"OKAYFREEDOM_INJECTED\" style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</div>",
